snippet.title: Rocket League Season 9 Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Watch the Season 9 Gameplay Trailer!
Learn more here: http://www.rocketleague.com/news/unleash-the-elements-in-season-9/

In a world of frost vs. flame, which will you choose? Unleash the mystical Emperor II, a new Car with twin Frozen and Scorched versions in Season 9’s Rocket Pass. Master the elements in a new Forbidden Temple Arena Variant, battle against other players to earn explosive Tournament Rewards, or customize your car with ice-cold Rocket Pass Items. 

Season 9 begins December 7! 

#RocketLeague #RocketPass #RocketLeagueSeason9
